Install instructions
---------------------

o Minimum required/tested versions:

  Linux kernel: 5.13
  clang: 13


o Ubuntu impish (21.10):

  sudo apt install clang llvm libbpf-dev libbpf0 dwarves
  sudo apt install linux-tools-common (for bpftool)

  mkdir build
  make


o Optional Docker build instructions:

  sudo apt install docker.io
  sudo adduser myuser docker

